observations.recommendation:
We recommended the following:
• The Municipal Treasurer should be granted cash advance only for salaries, wages, honoraria and petty operating expenses;
• A petty cash fund should be established for operating expenses of small amount;
• All disbursements exceeding ₱15,000.00 must be made by check direct to the payee;
• No cash advance should be granted to the Municipal Treasurer for implementation of infrastructure projects; and

We have recommended that Management:
 The Municipal Treasurer should be granted cash advance only for salaries, wages, honoraria and petty operating expenses;
